section_summary: The text is a transcript of a session in a council meeting. The speaker, Mr. Dawood, addresses the audience and expresses his intention to bring about change and represent the voice of the youth. He mentions the importance of focusing on the youth as they constitute two-thirds of the nation. He also mentions his previous advice to another individual, Mr. Bu Abdulaziz, to support a young candidate for a position. However, he expresses disappointment that no young candidates came forward. The session continues with a request for an extension of time. The text is from the legislative session on June 20, 2023.
